oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The N scavenging ability of winter turnip rape was investigated in a field experiment in 2009 and 2010 at the Viikki Experimental Farm (University of Helsinki, Finland). The experiment was arranged in a randomized complete block design with four replicates.
